title: Red Raiders move up in latest rankings - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Red Raiders move up in latest rankings - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: NEW ORLEANS, La. – The Texas Tech track and field team enter the rankings inside the top 7 in the fifth installment of the U.S. Track & Field and Cross Country Coaches Association (USTFCCCA) poll released Monday afternoon.
